author: crogers
msg: For BEEHIVE-1031, ScopedRequest.getNamesOfRemovableAttributes() returns names of attributes that do not need to be saved in a session or restored later for a follow up refresh request. They are not required for the refresh request. Use this to optimize the set of request attributes that may be stored in a user session and later restored as attributes for a refresh request.
The MockPortletTag class was updated to use this new method for our the mock portal tests.
